<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 1 (Leon) - Start</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リオン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Leon</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>スタン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stahn</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おのれ、強欲レンズハンターめ！
彼女を人質にとるとは、なんて卑劣な！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How dare that greedy Lens hunter!
It's pure cowardness to take her hostage!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>レンズってなんだろう？
このあたりじゃ聞いた事ない言葉だけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Did you say Lens?
I've haven't heard that word around these parts.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>というかさ、リオン。
「ものすごく、くすぐる」って
べつにたいした事じゃないよな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>On that note, Leon...
He said, "It'll make you laugh a ton".
Doesn't seem like a big deal, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Not sure about this one.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>彼女の身の安全には代えられない。
今は……奴に従うしかないか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Nothing is more important than her safety.
For right now... all I can do is whatever he asks.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だめだ、聞いてない……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No good, I guess. He didn't hear me...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>最初の要求は……行列の出来る店で
ピーチパイを手に入れてこいだと！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>His first demand is... to get a peach pie
from a shop with a long line?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんだか生ぬるい要求だなあ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's a pretty mild demand.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
